href="jms-001M.xml"
type="local"
addr="jms-001M">positive</fr:link> elements of a lifted dcpo <fr:tex>\mathsf { L } {A}</fr:tex> are exactly the <fr:em>defined</fr:em> elements, i.e. those lying in the image of <fr:tex>{ A } \xrightarrow {{ \eta }}{ \mathsf { L } {A} }</fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
